@prsephton 

> Will existing projects which use buildout continue to function if you change from eggs to wheels?

On Linux systems, and Mac Systems with compilers, sure:  `zope.interface` is trivial to compile.  On Windows, not so much.  Buildout will need to grow support for installing wheels (see https://github.com/buildout/buildout/issues/144).

