@PiOverFour:
Your PSD file is not technically a single layer PSD. It has a "background" layer which Photoshop saves in a composite image. True single layer PSD has a layer saved separately as well.

So, it's OK. And `PSDImage.bbox` is `None` because it's based on layers.

